tafsir[8]{c,v,t}:
  94,1,"Alla yaacnii ɓernde ma O yiɗnu ma jaɓɓaade wahyu."
  94,2,"Min njaafi ma ko yawti ko e bakkatuuji ma Min tellinan ma teddeendi balɗe jaahiliyya ɗe ngonnaɗa ɗe."
  94,3,"Oon tampinɗo ma haa keeci ɗesi helde."
  94,4,"Mi toownan ma jantawol ma, haa mbattuɗa inneede e noddinaandu e wuurnaandu e ka nanndi heen."
  94,5,"Sattaande ɓittere fof woni battane mum ko newuya e yaajeende e ittude nde."
  94,6,"Kala satteende e ɓittere na wondi e newaare e yaajeende, si a anndii ɗuum hulnataa ma wollo faloo noddaandu ma lorde yimɓe ma wollo falaade noddaandu Ma."
  94,7,"Si gaynii golle ma, kantinɗaa ɗe tiiɗna e dewal Alla."
  94,8,"Waɗ ndeereeru Ma e faandaare Ma faade e Alla gooto O."
